product_name: Woods Aluminum Double Roll-Up Table - 2012 Closeout
long_description: The Woods Aluminum Double Roll-Up Table collapses down and stows in an included carrying case, making it easy to take along on car-camping trips and picnics in the park. Adjustable leg length lets you level the table on uneven ground. Includes an extra storage compartment under the table. The Woods Aluminum Double Roll-Up Table folds down and fits in the included carrying case. Closeout.
